<h1 id="ability-title" class="text-left ml-5">Sinner's Sense</h1>
<p id="ability-text" class="text-left mx-5 mb-5">Your demonic blood tingles in the presence of demonic entities. You
  passively perceive demonic beings and things influenced by demons if they are within 20 ft of you, and have advantage
  on checks to identify them outside of 20 ft.</p>

